Title: Convert spatial bookmarks to layer
Abstract:
Converts stored spatial bookmarks to a polygon layer.

This algorithm creates a new layer containing polygon features for stored spatial bookmarks.

The export can be filtered to only bookmarks belonging to the current project, to all user bookmarks, or a combination of both.

Accepted data types.str: as string representation of int, e.g. '1'
layer ID. CRS of layer is used.
layer name. CRS of layer is used.
layer source. CRS of layer is used.
'memory:' to store result in temporary memory layer
using vector provider ID prefix and destination URI, e.g. 'postgres:…' to store result in PostGIS table
